title: CacheGetAllIds
name: CacheGetAllIds
description: this function return a array containing all keys inside the cache.

arguments.name: filter
arguments.description: key filter for the elements, the filter follow the same rules as for cfdirectory-filter.

arguments.name: cacheName
arguments.description: definition of the cache used by name, when not set the "default Object Cache" defined in Lucee Administrator is used instead.
